  "hypothesis": "An eight-query-head GQA group can preserve the measured multivalue-cluster arithmetic while broadcasting the shared key stream and collapsing eight identical value-replay streams to one external stream, removing the independent-head KV-bandwidth abstraction from the Llama7B frontier.",
